 \end{verbatim}
 then the wildcard expands to
 \begin{verbatim}
-/spad/mnt/linux/nalg/*.spad
+/spad/mnt/${SYS}/nalg/*.spad
 \end{verbatim}
 and all of the matching files would be recompiled.
